features: Efficient Laundry Room Makeover - Streamline your space and maximize storage. With a generous 40 oz capacity, it eliminates the need for bulky detergent containers, giving your laundry room a sleek and tidy appearance.

Upgrade Rust and Corrosion-resistant Lid:Featuring a stainless steel outer layer and a BPA-free plastic inner layer. Unlike traditional materials such as iron or wood, this cover is highly resistant to rust and can withstand long-term exposure to laundry detergent, fabric softener, and bleach. With the addition of a silicone seal, it offers excellent sealing properties, ensuring cleanliness and hygiene while preventing liquid spoilage.

Waterproof Laundry Labels:KitHero laundry organization set includes six waterproof labels for easy identification of detergent, softener, bleach, and two blank labels for personalized use. No more mixing up bottles and wasting time searching – stay organized and efficient!

Convenient Design:The wide mouth design makes it easier to pour in detergent, and it has a silicone sealing ring to prevent leakage. The unique V-shaped spout design ensures silky smooth pouring and precise control of the amount dispensed. Additionally, our dispensers feature convenient handles that allow for easy lifting and handling, making the entire process seamless and hassle-free. Perfect for everyday laundry needs!

High-Quality Glass and Dishwasher Safe: Crafted with high-quality borosilicate clear glass and equipped with rust-resistant glass lids，KitHero large laundry jars are built to last. Cleaning is easy whether you hand wash or machine wash.

Perfect Gift Ideal for Storage:KitHero laundry soap dispenser set is an ideal choice for house warming, weddings, anniversaries, special occasions, and Christmas. Give the gift of convenience and organization to your loved ones with this practical and stylish product.
